deps.context: project(llvm   version 8.0.0   languages c cxx asm)

libs.content: find_library(iconv_library_path names iconv libiconv libiconv-2 c)
find_program(gold_executable names ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld.gold ld.gold ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld ld doc "the gold linker")
find_program(ld64_executable names ld doc "the ld64 linker")

find_program(sphinx_executable
             names sphinx-build sphinx-build2
             doc "path to sphinx-build executable")

find_program(llvmar_executable
  names llvm-ar
  doc "the llvm-ar executable"
  )

find_program(llvmnm_executable
  names llvm-nm
  doc "the llvm-nm executable"
  )

find_program(llvmranlib_executable
  names llvm-ranlib
  doc "the llvm-ranlib executable"
  )
find_program(gold_executable names ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld.gold ld.gold ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld ld doc "the gold linker")

find_program(llvm_doxygen_qhelpgenerator_path qhelpgenerator
      doc "path to the qhelpgenerator binary")

find_program(llvm_lit
                   names llvm-lit lit.py lit
                   paths "${llvm_main_src_dir}/utils/lit"
                   doc "path to lit.py")
